author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
I was lucky to spend a lot of time with Roy Thomas Baker before, during and after he produced our second album, One Way Ticket To Hell..and Back.  He had a profound impact on my working practices, musical philosophy and life in general.  I haven't tried to include everything Roy did in this episode - that's not what this is for, but I did want to pay tribute to a man I loved. 

#roythomasbaker
title: Remembering Roy Thomas Baker
